  "text": "211 确实比 985 的笨很多\n我那些聪明考上 985 的同学\n在初高中的时候\n我就已经发现他们真的太聪明了\n只有真的努力过考不上 985\n才知道 985 的脑力含金量\n我就是那个努力过但是考不上的\nQuote\n铁手\n@0427SMtieshou\nI was chatting with a friend who's a 10-year HR veteran.\n\nI asked him if they only hire graduates from 211/985 schools?\n\nHe said no, we only take 985s.\n\nWhat about 211s?\nNo 211s, the brainpower gap with 985s is huge.\n\nDo they take all 985s?\nNo. During interviews, I'll screen out\n2:53 AM · Jun 5, 2026",
